        <p class="c18 title" id="h.thkap1zihpcn"><span class="c3 c13">Price Manager User Guide</span></p>
        <p class="c0"><span class="c11 c2">Price Manager is a fast solution for updating &#39;Price&#39; and &#39;Compare at price&#39; in bulk in your Shopify store.</span></p>
        <h4 class="c17" id="h.t98025ubnohu"><span class="c16">1. Filter or search for the products you wish to update.</span></h4>
        <p class="c1"><span class="c3 c15">Click the &lsquo;Sync&rsquo; button if you wish to enable advanced filtering.</span></p>
        <p class="c1"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 414.50px; height: 102.32px;"><img alt="" src="images/image2.png" style="width: 414.50px; height: 102.32px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p>
        <h4 class="c17" id="h.ih5m9qpbl2bh"><span class="c20 c21">2. Making Pricing updates</span></h4>
        <p class="c1"><span class="c20 c2 c22">For price increases or decrease select &lsquo;By&rsquo; in the second dropdown box.</span></p>
        <p class="c1 c5"><span class="c3 c15"></span></p>
        <p class="c1"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 794.00px; height: 80.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image3.png" style="width: 794.00px; height: 80.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p>
        <p class="c1"><span class="c3 c2">Use the guide below to perform pricing updates.</span></p>
        <p class="c1 c5"><span class="c3 c15"></span></p>
        <ul class="c7 lst-kix_cptag8lq42i5-0 start">
            <li class="c4 c10"><span class="c11 c2">Percentage increase. Use: &nbsp;+10%</span></li>
            <li class="c4 c10"><span class="c11 c2">Percentage decrease. Use: -10%</span></li>
            <li class="c4 c10"><span class="c2 c11">Increase by value. Use: &nbsp;+10</span></li>
            <li class="c4 c10"><span class="c11 c2">Decrease by value. Use: -10</span></li>
        </ul>
        <p class="c4"><span class="c11 c2">Check the box &lsquo;Apply to Compare at Price&rsquo; to apply the same update to the compare at price</span></p>
        <p class="c1"><span class="c20">To update the price to a specific value select &lsquo;To&rsquo; in the second dropdown box.</span></p>
        <p class="c1"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 794.00px; height: 74.67px;"><img alt="" src="images/image5.png" style="width: 794.00px; height: 74.67px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p>
        <p class="c1"><span class="c3 c2">Use the guide below to perform price updates.</span></p>
        <p class="c1 c5"><span class="c3 c15"></span></p>
        <ul class="c7 lst-kix_cptag8lq42i5-0">
            <li class="c1 c10"><span class="c2">Set price to $99. Use: 99</span></li>
            <li class="c4 c10"><span class="c11 c2">Set Compare at price to $99. Use: 99</span></li>
        </ul>
        <p class="c4"><span class="c11 c2">If you would like to copy the price of a selected group of products to &lsquo;Compare at Price&rsquo; or do the opposite you can select this action in the first dropdown.</span></p>
        <ul class="c7 lst-kix_cptag8lq42i5-0">
            <li class="c4 c10"><span class="c11 c2">Update Price with Compare at price </span></li>
        </ul>
        <p class="c4"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 794.00px; height: 216.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image1.png" style="width: 794.00px; height: 216.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p>
        <ul class="c7 lst-kix_cptag8lq42i5-0">
            <li class="c4 c10"><span class="c11 c2">Update Compare at price with Price</span></li>
        </ul>
        <p class="c4"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 794.00px; height: 202.67px;"><img alt="" src="images/image4.png" style="width: 794.00px; height: 202.67px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p>
        <p class="c12"><span class="c2">If you have any further questions or need help please contact us on live chat or send us an email at </span><span class="c2 c6"><a class="c14" href="mailto:support@aperitive.io">support@aperitive.io</a></span></p>
